                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310217-243-off1421 t18310217-243-cd1422"></join>, 2 half-crowns, 7 shillings, and 1 sixpence, the monies of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18310217-243-victim2244" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Smith
                        <interp inst="t18310217-243-victim2244" type="surname" value="Smith"></interp>
